What TapConverter Does

TapConverter is a fast, one-screen unit converter for everyday use, including:
• Length
• Weight
• Temperature
• Volume
• Area
• Speed
• Data
• Time

Common Questions

1) Conversions are not updating
• Make sure the input value is a valid number.
• Try changing the “From” and “To” units again.
• Force close and reopen the app.

2) Why don’t I see ads?
• Ads may not appear all the time.
• Ad availability depends on region, device, and network.
• If you recently installed, ad serving can take time.

3) Is my data synced to cloud?
• No. Conversion history is stored locally on your device.

4) How do I clear history?
• Open History 
